commitResults.messageTitle: Implement static GUI based on mockup
commitResults.messageBody:
* Create the following UI components:
    * MainWindow - the main app window, consisting of top section
      (header comprising of logo), left section (GraphicsSection),
      right section (CliSection)
    * GraphicsSection - the left section of the app displaying command
      execution results in illustration
    * CliSection - the right section of the app which accepts user input
      commands and displays system response messages from the execution
      of commands
    * ModuleList - sub-section within the GraphicsSection displaying the
      modules added by the user

* Note that this commit only implements the GUI statically (changes to
  FXML & CSS files); no dynamic content can be displayed yet.

* Implement skeletal structure of controllers attached to FXML
  components for implementation of dynamic GUI in future commits.
